           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-rig    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-cor-reg-900.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-cor-reg-400.
       acc-cor-reg-500.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Prezzo unitario                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
