      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-scm-loc-ccp-loc    to   w-scm-loc-ccp-wlc      .
       scm-loc-ccp-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Identificazione Cap                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se Cap corretto                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
